<br>
-Summon as many creatures as possible before the combat. (Planater, Deva, etc.)<br>
-Imoen, Aerie and Jan should cast energy blades before the combat.<br>
-One of melees should equip the cloak of mirroring to deflect beholders' gazes.<br>
-Aerie (dual class mage/cleric) should use spell trigger to cast clerical buffs. (bless, chant and defensive harmony.)<br>
-Imoen, Aerie and Jan should use (chain) contingency to cast improved haste on themselves. Aerie should also cast holy power on herself.<br>
<br>
